Whisp

3 HP, 4 AP, 2 MP, -pdef, 2mdef

*Whisp can only be hurt by magic attacks*

Shocking Touch: 3 AP: Whisp can move through an occupied space until its next turn. 
      When whisp and another creature (hero or monster) occupy the same space, whisp attacks with 2mE (2 magic Elemental)

Glow: 4 AP: create light radius of 2 squares.
    In "Blind" this can activate other monsters
    
